description: Learn how to make this easy jacket potato recipe that’s perfect for a meat-free Monday.
keywords: Jacket potato,Pescatarian,Low salt,Gluten free,Tree nut free,Egg free,Sesame free,Potato,Fish,High protein,Soy free,Wheat free,Avocado,Peanut free
name: Baked Jacket Potatoes Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 1 large avocado, peeled and finely diced
185g can tuna in oil, drained and flaked

recipeInstructions.text: Prick potatoes 6-8 times with a skewer. Put onto a baking tray and bake for 45 minutes or until soft. Cool slightly. Halve potatoes, scoop out flesh and roughly mash.
Add tuna, corn, avocado and chives. Stir until well combined. Season with salt and pepper.
Spoon mixture into potato shells. Sprinkle with cheese and bake for 15-20 minutes or until cheese is melted and golden. Serve with salad.
